  <div class="outcome">
    <div class="outcome-eyebrow">Sean&apos;s win</div>
    <h2 class="outcome-title">The flag finally changes the service. The kit finally meets him in a venue he trusts. The cohort the system has known about for a decade is finally the cohort the system actually holds.</h2>
    <p class="outcome-body">Sean does not see policy. He sees his brother at the kitchen table, a kit he can use, and a system that, for the first time, met him where he is. <strong>The avoidable death that does not happen is the avoidable death that the system finally chose not to allow.</strong> The access story sustains.</p>
